<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>أَن يَقُول للْمُدَّعى أَلَك بَيِّنَة<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>أَي حجَّة<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
